(fC^{\prime})^{\prime}r+(1\pm i\omega r_{0}\pm i\omega r)fC^{\prime}+(fC)^{\prime}(\pm i\omega r-1\pm i\omega r_{0})\pm i\omega\frac{r_{0}}{r}fC+\frac{\omega^{2}}{f}C\frac{r_{0}^{2}}{r}(2-\frac{r_{0}^{2}}{r^{2}})-l(l+1)\frac{C}{r}=0
