\partial_{z}(z^{2}f\partial_{z}C)\pm2i\omega(1+r_{0}z)(-f\partial_{z}C)\pm i\omega(1+r_{0}z)(-\partial_{z}fC)+z\partial_{z}fC\pm i\omega r_{0}fC+\frac{\omega^{2}r_{0}^{2}}{f}(2-r_{0}^{2}z^{2})C-l(l+1)C=0
