\pm2i\omega(-C_{1})\pm2i\omega r_{0}C_{0}+2\omega^{2}r_{0}^{2}C_{0}-l(l+1)C_{0}=0\Longrightarrow C_{1}=-[\frac{l(l+1)}{\pm2i\omega}+r_{0}(-1\pm i\omega r_{0})]C_{0}
